Usage: set_wire_load_selection_group [-help] <wireload_selection_group_name>
                                     [<list_of_instances>]
                                     [-library <library_name>] [-max] [-min]

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
<wireload_selection_group_name>     # Specifies the name of the wireload
                                    # selection group (string, required)
<list_of_instances>                 # Specify the list of instances
                                    # (string, optional)
-library <library_name>             # Specifies the name of the technology
                                    # library to search for the wireload
                                    # selection table (string, optional)
-max                                # Controls the choice of a wireload
                                    # selection table only for the PVT max
                                    # corner (bool, optional)
-min                                # Controls the choice of a wireload
                                    # selection table only for the minimum PVT
                                    # corner (bool, optional)